Reverse a String – Write a program to reverse a given string.
Check Palindrome – Write a program to check whether a string is a palindrome.
Find the Factorial of a Number – Calculate the factorial of a given number using recursion or iteration.
Prime Number – Write a program to check whether a number is prime or not.
Fibonacci Sequence – Print the Fibonacci sequence up to a given number or nth term.
Count Vowels and Consonants – Count the number of vowels and consonants in a given string.
Count the Frequency of Each Character in a String – Count the occurrences of each character in a string.
Armstrong Number – Write a program to check if a number is an Armstrong number.
Sum of Natural Numbers – Calculate the sum of the first N natural numbers.
Find the Largest/Smallest Element in an Array – Write a program to find the largest or smallest number in an array.